isTNG simulation. Future observations with the\nJames Webb Space Telescope will be able to measure Z_emiss for 4 other GRB\nhosts with known Z_abs values, using ~2 hour observations. While small, the\nsample will provide preliminary constraints on the Z_abs-Z_emiss relation to\ntest chemical enrichment schemes in cosmological simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2021 01:42:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-30"}
