oming Square-Kilometer Array\n(SKA). Additionally, since real-time analysis can be performed, only data with\npromising detections can be saved to disk, providing a solution to the big-data\nproblem that modern astronomy is dealing with.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2021 08:29:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 09:19:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 13:30:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-09"}
