htly regulates the fueling of host\nnucleus. Our findings may have wider implications, particularly in the context\nof outflow/jet dynamics, and radio-AGN feedback, associated with these massive\ngalaxies in the contemporary Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2021 11:27:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-30"}
