xpansion to address magnetic field effects in complex settings as heavy-ion\ncollisions, the early universe, and magnetars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2021 14:42:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-30"}
